  "text": "Eq. (34) through Eq. (38) also hold for semi-fixed processes in general, if as usual throughout those equations we replace σ v with σ v and replace ∆I v with ∆I v . However, Eqs. [CITATION_1] and [CITATION_2] along with the associated IFTs need not hold for semi-fixed processes in general.",
